확인¶

  • 일하는 날 (working day:1) 8, 17,18시에 많은 빌리고,
  • 휴일의 경우(working day:1) 12~16시에 많다.
  • 주중(dayofweek:0,1,2,3,4) 8, 17,18시에 많은 빌리고,
  • 주말(dayofweek:5,6) 11~16시에 많다.

Score = Root Mean Squared Logarithmic Error, RMSLE.

$$ \sqrt{\frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^n (\log(p_i + 1) - \log(a_i+1))^2 } $$

RMSE 함수 생성¶

In [41]:
import numpy as np
from sklearn.metrics import make_scorer

def rmsle(predict, actual):
    predict = np.array(predict)  # 예측값
    actual = np.array(actual)    # 실제값
    
    # log가 아닐 경우 
    #log_pred = np.log(predict + 1)  # log (예측값+1)
    #log_actual = np.log(actual + 1) # log (실제값+1)
    
    # y_train이 log일 경우, 
    log_pred = predict + 1
    log_actual = actual + 1
    
    diff = log_pred - log_actual # log(예측값+1) - log(실제값+1)
    square_diff = diff ** 2      # diff * diff
    mean_square_diff = square_diff.mean()  # (diff * diff)/n
    
    score = np.sqrt(mean_square_diff) 
    
    return score
In [43]:
rmsle_scorer = make_scorer(rmsle)
rmsle_scorer
Out[43]:
make_scorer(rmsle)

교차 평가 시행- cross validation¶

  • cross_val_score(estimator, X, y=None, scoring=평가기준, cv=None)
  • cv를 이용하여 x,y data를 분할하고 estimator를 넣어
  • scoring metric를 구하는 과정을 반복(cv의 값만큼)
score1 = cross_val_score(model,    # 적용 모델 
                          X_train, # X 데이터 셋(학습용)
                         y_train,  # y 데이터 셋(학습용)
                         cv=20,    # cv : 20 
                         scoring=rmsle_scorer).mean()
In [51]:
from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score

# y_train에 log을 씌움
score = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, cv=20, scoring=rmsle_scorer).mean()
